window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Waking up at the foot of your own grave is no picnic…especially when you can’t remember how you got there. </p> <p>Cursed with powers she can’t name, Sloane Cabot has vowed to catch the Rogue who turned her into a monster and killed her family. Too bad a broodingly hot mage is bound to keep her on the straight and narrow. </p> <p>Whether she likes it or not....</p>"; 
